Company Introduction



                                    Building ScaleListed on the Main Board of The Singapore Exchange in 2001, Willas-Array Electronics (Holdings) Limited was founded in 1981 and has since grown to become one of the largest premier distributors of electronic components. Riding along the wave of economic globalization, we have opened offices in PRC, Singapore, Malaysia, South Korea and Taiwan. As an early mover in the PRC, we have ...
                                

                                        Building Scale
Listed on the Main Board of The Singapore Exchange in 2001, Willas-Array Electronics (Holdings) Limited was founded in 1981 and has since grown to become one of the largest premier distributors of electronic components. Riding along the wave of economic globalization, we have opened offices in PRC, Singapore, Malaysia, South Korea and Taiwan. As an early mover in the PRC, we have successfully penetrated the market to capitalize on its growth opportunities. With a network of offices strategically located in major cities like Beijing, Qingdao, Shanghai, Chengdu, Xiamen, Guangzhou and Shenzhen, as well as bonded warehoues in the Free Trade Zone in Shanghai and Shenzhen, we are commited to provide excellent services to our PRC customers.

Delivering Solutions
Willas-Array is distinguished not only in "Scale" but also in "Solutions". Our highly qualified and experienced field application engineers and technical support specialists are reputed for their ability to deliver quality and cost-effective reference designs to customers. To forge ahead our business as a solutions provider, we have set up an Application and Development Division in Hong Kong and Guangzhou. For the past years, we have established a long-standing relationship with the enterprises which have well reputation in the industry. Apart from functioning as a distributor of high quality products, we also have the technical expertise, which can strengthen our customers' competitive advantages in the market.

At Willas-Array, we make success happen.
                                    


