Company Description                    




                        
Willas-Array Electronics (Holdings) Limited engaged in the distribution of electronic components. The company's product lines includes microprocessors, discrete, analog, digital, memory, optoelectronics, sensor, passive, LED light source among others. Willas-Array Electronics products are used in audio/video, telecommunications, industrial, consumer and computer industries. The company's main markets are in China with a network of offices in Beijing, Qingdao, Shanghai, Chengdu, Xiamen, Guangzhou, Shenzhen, Zhongshan and Taiwan as well as bonded warehouse in Waigaoqiao (Shanghai) and taxed warehouse in Jinqiao (Shanghai). Willas-Array Electronics was established in 1981, listed on the Main Board of The Singapore in 2001 and Exchange and Hong Kong Stock Exchange 2013. The company's headquarter is located in Hong Kong.                    


